869	  Iter-046 closes the producer chain end-to-end. Combined with iter-043's curve consumer, the H$^0$ Module.Finite ladder $\Module.\mathrm{Finite}\,k\,(\HModule\,k\,(\toModuleKSheaf\,C)\,0)$ is now closed for proper integral $\Spec k$-schemes --- and in particular for the smooth proper geometrically irreducible curves that the project's protected declarations consume.
